---
const principles = [
  ['Enjoyment leads to progress', ', validated processes for stress free progression'],
  ['Invitation, not intimidation', ', no partner or experience required'],
  ['Growth over performance', ', confidence, presence, real friendships'],
  ['Choice and inclusivity', ', roles by curiosity, not gender'],
];
---

<section id="garden-intro-v2" style="background: white; padding: 70px 20px;">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <div
        style="font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px;"
      >
        Our Philosophy
      </div>
      <h2
        style="font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700; color: #4E5D22; margin-bottom: 25px; line-height: 1.2;"
      >
        Why Tango Garden
      </h2>
      <p
        style="font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 500; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.4;"
      >
        Because many young people are craving connection, not performance.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 60px;">
      <div
        style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; color: #444; text-align: center; max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto;"
      >
        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
          Tango Garden was created for people who want to meet others in real life, feel at home in
          their bodies, and grow through shared experience.
        </p>
        <p>
          In a world of gyms, apps, and quick interactions, we choose to build something slower and
          more human, a place where you can show up alone, be welcomed immediately, and belong over
          time.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most of our students are young adults navigating work, relationships, and identity,
          looking for a place that feels genuine and warm.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        style="background: #F3EDE1; border-radius: 20px; padding: 60px 40px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.05);"
      >
        <div
          style="position: absolute; top: -20px; right: -20px; font-size: 120px; opacity: 0.05; color: #4E5D22; pointer-events: none;"
        >
          🌿
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
          <h3 style="font-size: 28px; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px;">
            Our Principles
          </h3>
          <p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px;">Here, tango is the vehicle, not the goal.</p>
        </div>

        <div
          style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;"
        >
          {
            principles.map(([bold, rest]) => (
              <div class="garden-value-item">
                <span class="garden-check">✓</span>
                <strong>{bold}</strong>
                {rest}
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
